name: Kabutops
author: Shin Nagasawa
flavor_text: Its body had begun to change so it could function on land. But it didn’t adapt in time and went extinct.

abilities.name: Fossilized Memories
abilities.effect: As long as this Pokémon is your Active Pokémon, your opponent can’t play any Supporter cards from their hand.

attacks.name: Rock Slide
attacks.effect: This attack does 20 damage to 2 of your opponent’s Benched Pokémon. (Don’t apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokémon.)
